<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3743] Throttle major compaction</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3743</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add the ability to throttle major compaction.&lt;br/&gt;
For those use cases when a stop-the-world approach is not practical, it is useful to be able to throttle the impact that major compaction has on the cluster.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
